## Prerequisites

- **cmake 3.25+** - Build system generator ([installation guide](https://cmake.org/download/))
- **C++{{cpp_standard}} compiler** - GCC 14+ or Clang 18+ ([GCC](https://gcc.gnu.org/) | [LLVM/Clang](https://releases.llvm.org/))
- **just** - Command runner ([installation guide](https://github.com/casey/just#installation))

The following validation tools are also required:

| Tool | Purpose | Install |
|------|---------|---------|
| [clang-format](https://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormat.html) | Code formatting | `brew install clang-format` |
| [clang-tidy](https://clang.llvm.org/extra/clang-tidy/) | Static analysis / linting | `brew install llvm` |
| [cppcheck](https://cppcheck.sourceforge.io/) | Static analysis | `brew install cppcheck` |
| [flawfinder](https://dwheeler.com/flawfinder/) | Security scanning | `brew install flawfinder` |
| [include-what-you-use](https://include-what-you-use.org/) | Include hygiene (advisory) | `brew install include-what-you-use` |
| [codespell](https://github.com/codespell-project/codespell) | Spell checking | `brew install codespell` |
| [semgrep](https://semgrep.dev/) | Custom static analysis | `brew install semgrep` |
| [lcov](https://github.com/linux-test-project/lcov) | Code coverage reporting | `brew install lcov` |

